content.text: *Physical World* is an ongoing collection of illustrated scenes and small objects and characters from those scenes, taking place in an unknown world parallel to our own. No better and no worse. New pieces are made every month, delivered to patreon subscribers in the form of prints and stickers, since 2022.

content.text: *Bear Fighter Pilot* 2025 - Shot down and unsure of itself, the bear wasn't trained for this. Radio silence on every frequency. The bear is alone.

*Zach Hazard Vaupen* sometimes also known as Emo Sludge is a NY-based artist who enjoys creating images, games, and stories through various digital mediums. His artwork has traveled the world, and maybe someday he will too.
